    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069300/extras/3f3de21601b96b6c84098bf375dfd683.avif?t=1759510606\" width=534 height=110 /></span><br>After a science experiment goes wrong, it's up to you, Morgan Pigman, to save the world from a laboratory disaster. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069300/extras/d8eff0051de570ebde3ecea4aea81503.avif?t=1759510606\" width=534 height=121 /></span><br>Wild fireballs have gone haywire, and you must shoot them down using your special hookshot. Shoot the hookshot straight upwards to attach it to the ceiling, where it will stay briefly, destroying any fireballs that touch the hanging rope. Gain access to various powerups, such as freezing movement, replenishing countdown time, faster shots, upgraded defenses, and more. <br><br>Can you clear each level before time runs out without getting turned into roasted ham? <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069300/extras/7717289f0dd4e119f76a294e143ae246.avif?t=1759510606\" width=534 height=126 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Puzzle action shooting gameplay<br></li><li>2D bouncing fireball physics<br></li><li>Gain different power-ups<br></li><li>Exciting electronic dance music</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069300/extras/6f3dd983febb88764bf74852c89459f7.avif?t=1759510606\" width=480 height=162 /></span>",
